text: Joseph Ellis Pasquale (born 20 August 1961) is an English comedian, actor and television presenter who is best known for his high-pitched voice. He won the fourth series of I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here! in 2004 and appeared in the eighth series of Dancing on Ice in 2013. == References == Category:English comedians Category:1961 births Category:Living people
